						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone in front of the temple close to the village Chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>Siṅghaṇa—A.D. 1223.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated in the king's regnal <hi rend="bold">year 14, Svabhānu, Mārgasira, ba. Amāvāsyā, Sunday.</hi> The details correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1223, December 23,</hi> which was a Saturday, not Sunday and the <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> ended at ·59 on that day.</p>						

						<p>The inscription records the death of a hero (name lost) probably of <hi rend="bold">Huligere.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
