<!--<h4>First Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇa pratāpa cakravartti
<lb n="2"/>śrī siṁhaṇadē<unclear>va</unclear>varuṣada 14 neya svabhānu saṁvatsara 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>da mārggaśira bahuḷa Amavāse Ādivāradalu hulige<unclear>ṟe</unclear> sāha
<lb n="4" break="no"/><ce>worn out</ce>
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> suralōka prāptanāda śrī
</p>

